# SimpleAdding:

# Have the function SimpleAdding(num) add up all the numbers from 1 to num. For the test cases, the parameter num will be any number     
  from 1 to 1000.

def SimpleAdding(num):
    sum=0
    for x in range(1,num+1):
        sum = sum + x
    return sum


SimpleAdding(50) 

Output: 1275
          
